      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense but it's still frustrating. it basically feels like these hidden costs are just eating away at my progress before i even get a chance to make a dent in the actual debt. is there a specific math formula you can show me? like, how does the bank actually figure out that specific interest number every single month?",
